uses OCR on screen to get your pokemon’s IV

attachments.text: GoIV seamlessly integrates into Pokemon GO making it easy to check all of your Pokemon's IVs! What are IVs? IVs, also known as Individual Values are hidden stats each Pokemon has that affects its total power. IVs are broken into 3 stats, Attack/Defense/Stamina and range from the values 0-15. A perfect Pokemon would have 15 in every stat. IVs are hidden and can only be discovered by using your Pokemon's CP, HP, and Level and running it through multiple formulas. GoIV makes the process easy, so you can spend more time catching Pokemon and less time worrying if they are strong! [FEATURES] • Automatically appears when on the Pokemon screen - disappears when not. • OCR to pull as much data as possible • Accurate IV ratings using HP, CP and exact Pokemon levels GoIV is not affiliated with Pokemon GO or Niantic in anyway. GoIV does NOT break any TOS issued by Niantic.
